Runnable        () -> void: executa o actiunem fara input/output
Supplier<T>     () -> T : produce o valoare
Consumer<T>     T -> void : consuma o valoare, nu intoarce nimic
Function<T,R>   T -> R : transforma un input in output
Predicate<T>    T -> boolean : testeaza o conditie
Comparator<T>   (T,T) -> int : compara doua valori pentru sortare